{"tid":835684,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個必須知嘅法律［可免則免］","createTime":"2018-09-25T05:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T07:38:47.000Z","uid":57396,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"09ad0ad1614384afe32f0fc8d5406fd615ac700a","tid":835684,"uid":57396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"平時好多野都可能犯緊罪，只係自己唔察覺 <br />\n可能衰左都唔知自己衰乜，返學又冇教<br />\n想理論 庭上個官又會話你：即係仲未知錯啦，仲未反省啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望個post幫到自己又幫到大家<br />\n可免則免 唔好比位人入<br />\n從日常到工作可能會唔小心中招嘅地方<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最近好無辜地惹上官非，心感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直都係良民，最怕惹麻煩嘅人<br />\n甚至乎連黑警講嘅野都信 事後先知口供紙嘅重要性"},{"pid":"db7e24bf52c1cf0ecc9e9a33df3c1f5b8b0605e7","tid":835684,"uid":145779,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"磚都無舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6711a1fc3ece70060427aaf12da5755358801801","tid":835684,"uid":57396,"like":48,"dislike":3,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"db7e24bf52c1cf0ecc9e9a33df3c1f5b8b0605e7","tid":835684,"uid":145779,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"磚都無舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠<br />\n<br />\n早前無啦啦係街比個醉酒mk打左幾拳，成身血，鼻骨都裂埋，仲見佢想出手，所以當時出手反擊，朋友報警，警察到場後連我都比人拉埋<br />\n<br />\n當時警察同我講，cctv影到，認左單嘢嘅話轉頭就放我走得<br />\n點知...係臭格坐左2日...<br />\n<br />\n我被告公眾地方打架，因口供紙衰，單野冇得避<br />\n<br />\n香港地有還擊就係錯，冇自衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efa91188491143a5ea4a62d280972cc21d1a796","tid":835684,"uid":35330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6711a1fc3ece70060427aaf12da5755358801801","tid":835684,"uid":57396,"like":48,"dislike":3,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"db7e24bf52c1cf0ecc9e9a33df3c1f5b8b0605e7","tid":835684,"uid":145779,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"磚都無舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自膠<br />\n<br />\n早前無啦啦係街比個醉酒mk打左幾拳，成身血，鼻骨都裂埋，仲見佢想出手，所以當時出手反擊，朋友報警，警察到場後連我都比人拉埋<br />\n<br />\n當時警察同我講，cctv影到，認左單嘢嘅話轉頭就放我走得<br />\n點知...係臭格坐左2日...<br />\n<br />\n我被告公眾地方打架，因口供紙衰，單野冇得避<br />\n<br />\n香港地有還擊就係錯，冇自衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"有冇認到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c5639997bd3dae33661d152ededcbe8fcab292","tid":835684,"uid":166474,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"唔識法律，但好肯定惹上官非係差館千祈乜野都唔好講，一黎講多錯多，二黎冇義務幫差佬查案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3fca2e8a27656e11bbbe18aaa94b56ae960e41","tid":835684,"uid":176888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"More 磚"},{"pid":"dad6c4de4dfd57d07f09cd1be368fefd3e969505","tid":835684,"uid":57396,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote